Crash Test Program
Author: D. Coderre
Date: 4.09.2015

Brief: Try to reproduce crashes in CAENVMElib driver by 
       looping common CAEN functions.

Install: 

	 - Install CAEN A2818 or A3818 HW and driver (see caen.it)
	 - Install CAENVMElib (tested with 2.41)
	 - Download this software. 
	 - make

Run:
	- Adjust enums in main.cc as wanted
	- make
	- ./crash_test
	- Recommend running in debugger
